<br>
The latest PvP changes are also to have been expected, and SOE was wise to also target other classes with disproportionate damage. <br>
<br>
I will agree with most disgruntled wizards on one front, though. The proper solution would have been to give other classes similar abilities, rather than undo the power that Wizards (and later, Paladins, Shadowknights, Rangers, etc.) wielded. Monk Feign Death is another great example of the reactionary nature of SOE as of late and speaks to the fact that the people at the helm now are largely those who disliked the original Brad McQuaid vision of high-powered content and high-powered adventurers.<br>
<br>
