<br>
1) &quot;Manaburn was nerfed for PoP.&quot; That's nice. CoH, levitation and a half dozen other spells are turned off in zones where they'll be a problem. The dev team has NEVER shown any hesitation in doing this before. Accepting the notion that the Manaburn nerf was just about PoP absolutely ignores the rest of EQ history. The story is implausible. And given that NO ONE USES MANABURN IN POP ANYWAY, it's hardly something to keep trotting out because, guess what, if that's what the dev team's intention was -- somehow keeping MB as a valuable tool in PoP -- they failed, and miserably.<br>
<br>
2) &quot;Stop complaining about MB being nerfed, beause it had to be due to the ebil Team MB.&quot; Well, no, actually, not. The people who are most strident about this seem to accept that even though the problems that they'd heard about never happened on their server, they surely were happening on all the rest.  Yeah, that makes sense. If I got 100 people to spam EQ boards talking about the giant chickens running around Freeport, would you assume that just because you didn't see any giant chickens there, that they just were mysteriously absent on your server? No, you wouldn't. Take the fishhook out of your mouth, please. And secondly, even if it did have to be nerfed (and honestly, it was a little too good -- any time something is a &quot;must have,&quot; it's pretty clearly in that category) it's not a binary choice: It's not leave it alone or turn it into the giant piece of shit it is today. There is a wide range of middle ground. No one seriously thinks that MB should be put back exactly the way it was, but that also doesn't mean you should bend over and accept what was done. Middle ground, seriously. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=artillis>Artillis</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_redspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Arcanist<BR>Enjoys Sheep Erotica</span><br>  Posts: 1764<br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/27/03 4:27:13 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26274.topic&index=14>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: re:</span><hr size=1> I agree with whizbang on his points.  Manaburn needed to be nerfed with the only 1 cast on a mob per minute type of thing and it needed to be flagged uncastable in some 